snippet.title: Karting Superstars - Official Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Every racing legend had an origin. For many, the origin was karting! From the creators of Circuit Superstars, Karting Superstars is an ode to the purest form of racing, where drivers compete in a close encounter of speed and precision. Let's race!

Karting Superstars is available on Steam Early Access NOW! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2503220/Karting_Superstars/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=early-access
